  "prompt": "What are some good English song with good music?",
  "response": "Here\u2019s a list of English songs with great music across various genres and eras. These songs are celebrated for their melodies, instrumentation, and production:\n\n### Rock/Pop Classics:\n1. **\"Bohemian Rhapsody\" - Queen**  \n   - A masterpiece blending rock, opera, and ballad styles with epic instrumentation.\n\n2. **\"Hotel California\" - Eagles**  \n   - Iconic guitar riffs and a haunting melody.\n\n3. **\"Imagine\" - John Lennon**  \n   - A timeless piano-driven ballad with a powerful message.\n\n4. **\"Stairway to Heaven\" - Led Zeppelin**  \n   - A legendary rock anthem with intricate guitar work.\n\n5. **\"Hey Jude\" - The Beatles**  \n   - A soothing melody with a memorable sing-along chorus.\n\n### Contemporary Pop/Ballads:\n6. **\"Rolling in the Deep\" - Adele**  \n   - A soulful track with a powerful vocal performance and rich instrumentation.\n\n7. **\"Shape of You\" - Ed Sheeran**  \n   - A catchy, upbeat melody with a groovy rhythm.\n\n8. **\"All of Me\" - John Legend**  \n   - A heartfelt piano ballad with emotional depth.\n\n9. **\"Someone Like You\" - Adele**  \n   - A minimalist yet powerful piano-driven song.\n\n### Electronic/Pop:\n10. **\"Wake Me Up\" - Avicii**  \n    - A fusion of folktronica and EDM with a memorable melody.\n\n11. **\"Lean On\" - Major Lazer & DJ Snake ft. M\u00d8**  \n    - A global hit with a catchy beat and infectious rhythm.\n\n12. **\"Clarity\" - Zedd ft. Foxes**  \n    - A beautifully produced EDM track with ethereal vocals.\n\n### R&B/Soul:\n13. **\"Ain't No Sunshine\" - Bill Withers**  \n    - A soulful classic with minimalist instrumentation.\n\n14. **\"Redbone\" - Childish Gambino**  \n    - A smooth, funky track with a retro vibe.\n\n15. **\"Blame It on the Boogie\" - The Jacksons**  \n    - A groovy disco classic with infectious energy.\n\n### Indie/Folk:\n16. **\"Ho Hey\" - The Lumineers**  \n    - A feel-good folk track with a catchy acoustic melody.\n\n17. **\"Skinny Love\" - Bon Iver**  \n    - A hauntingly beautiful acoustic song.\n\n18. **\"Home\" - Edward Sharpe & The Magnetic Zeros**  \n    - A joyful, folksy anthem with a sing-along chorus.\n\n### Hip-Hop/Rap:\n19. **\"Lose Yourself\" - Eminem**  \n    - A motivational rap anthem with a powerful beat.\n\n20. **\"Sicko Mode\" - Travis Scott**  \n    - A dynamic, genre-blending track with intricate production.\n\nThese songs showcase a variety of styles and eras, so you\u2019re likely to find something that resonates with your taste!",
